## Interactive Map Using Leaflet

Here's an interactive map I created using the **leaflet** package in R.

```{r leaflet-map, echo=FALSE}
library(leaflet)

leaflet() %>%
  addTiles() %>%
  addMarkers(lng = 77.5946, lat = 12.9716, popup = "Bangalore!")
